Program: Omnibus
Title: Belize
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jgd
Last Broadcast Date: 29 October 1987
Accompanying the Queens Own Highlanders on their tour of duty in Belize. Their role there is to assist the government in defending the country from external attacks, particularly at the border with Guatamala. Includes interviews with Prime Minister Manuel Esquivel and British army officer Peter Grant Peterkin. Show less